# Restore Instructions for Backup backup_20250818_221851

## To restore from this backup:

1. Stop all Claude Code Optimizer services:
   ```bash
   pkill -f 'claude-code-session-monitor'
   pkill -f 'continuous_monitor'
   ```

2. Restore databases:
   ```bash
   cd /Users/supabowl/Library/Mobile Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/BHT Promo iCloud/Organized AI/Windsurf/Claude Code Optimizer
   cp /Users/supabowl/Library/Mobile Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/BHT Promo iCloud/Organized AI/Windsurf/Claude Code Optimizer/database_backup/backup_20250818_221851/databases/*.db ./
   ```

3. Restore configuration files:
   ```bash
   cp -r /Users/supabowl/Library/Mobile Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/BHT Promo iCloud/Organized AI/Windsurf/Claude Code Optimizer/database_backup/backup_20250818_221851/files/config/* ./config/
   cp -r /Users/supabowl/Library/Mobile Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/BHT Promo iCloud/Organized AI/Windsurf/Claude Code Optimizer/database_backup/backup_20250818_221851/files/data/* ./data/
   ```

4. Verify database integrity:
   ```bash
   python migrations/verify_restore.py --backup-id backup_20250818_221851
   ```

5. Restart services:
   ```bash
   python start_smart_monitoring.sh
   ```
